{"tid":2442753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"偷食事件後復出 許志安4月拍台劇兼唱主題曲","createTime":"2021-03-11T14:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T14:56:25.000Z","uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"87d6028888becc6284ccd01318aa12183a0716ae","tid":2442753,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bdk_KsrKwoUprd6Ln5xnlA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-03/14056fe0-824f-11eb-bbf9-e945e2e61d8e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fbdk_KsrKwoUprd6Ln5xnlA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-03%2F14056fe0-824f-11eb-bbf9-e945e2e61d8e&h=0bc8519e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌手許志安（安仔）於2019年與黃心穎發生偷食事件後，停工了一段長時間，雖然去年曾上ViuTV節目《Chill Club》獻唱，但只是為復出試水溫。直到早前他預告將會全面復出，據知有3年沒有演戲的他，4月將會飛往台灣拍攝劇集《接招吧！製作人》，該劇是一套講述歌手奮鬥史為題材，以多個單元串成一個故事，演出的歌手還有周華健、蕭煌奇等，而安仔負責其中一個單元，此外，他還會唱劇集主題曲。<br />\n<br />\n有指安仔去年接到台灣電視台的邀請，既開心又緊張，但對復出的工作很謹慎，最終睇完劇本後覺得好喜歡，認為劇本好正面，遂決定答應演出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0UBjGGplScP_VE6J1aePAQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-03/3de97770-824f-11eb-bfff-2a85ff904722\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F0UBjGGplScP_VE6J1aePAQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-03%2F3de97770-824f-11eb-bfff-2a85ff904722&h=36f45cd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14bea2de76eca4dcf33417d88bcba00967d75caf","tid":2442753,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"安心出行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d79cfc4dbe853a073b8871f39d05c1c4f4722e","tid":2442753,"